Program: The Documentary
Title: Moscow on Thames
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p020r2wq
Last Broadcast Date: Sat 21 Jun 2014
More and more wealthy Russians are settling in London. From a lavish Russian Ball at the Royal Albert Hall to home-buying in the capital's most exclusive postcodes - Kensington - Olga Betko enters the world of work and play of the Russian business elite to find out why London has become a favourite destination. (Photo: A Russian Flag is waved. Credit: Harry Engels/Getty Images) Show less